OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWhile still very warm,
OL,6,Ftemperatures will be a little lower
OL,7,Fthan on previous days. Further periods
OL,8,Fof sunshine will develop, perhaps hazy
OL,9,Fand eventually sparking scattered
OL,10,Fshowers.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cloudy evening with
OL,13,Fshowers, some of which may turn
OL,14,Fthundery at times. Temperatures remain
OL,15,Fwarm overnight. Winds southwesterly
OL,16,Fand light but breezy along the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
