OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FFresher conditions spreading
OL,6,Fto all parts into Sunday, with
OL,7,Fsunshine and showers. More seasonable
OL,8,Ftemperatures than expected. Winds
OL,9,Fmoderate southwesterly.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,12,Fis looking dry and settled. Turning
OL,13,Fmore unsettled on Tuesday with
OL,14,Fsunshine and showers. Wednesday starts
OL,15,Fof sunny, then clouding over with rain
OL,16,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
